keyinsights.text: GTN has decreased  by 9%  from Q1-18 to Q4-19 due to increase in rebate by  19% by Payer 1
Cost of Sales has increased by 1.35% due to a change in COGS component from 18% to 23% and Profit Sharing from 21% to 24% during 19-Q1
Gross Contracted Sales has increased by 4% due to an increase in Units sold during by 345 M units Q1’19 – Q4’19
Reserves has decreased by 1.5% due to a change in Distribution component from 18% to 15% and Site of Care reserves from 21% to 19% during 19-Q1
